\begin{align*}
2z^2+13z+21&=(2z+a)(z+b)\\
&=2z^2+2zb+az+zb+ab\\
&=2z^2+(2b+a)z+(ab+z^2b)\\
&=2z^2+13z+21
\end{align*}
Equating the coefficients, we can see that
\begin{align*}
&2b+a=13\\
&ab+b=21
\end{align*}
